
// The code snippet adds a node to the [.session] node using the [add] slot. It creates a nested structure where a [role] node with the value "system" and a [content] node are added. The [content] node's value is retrieved from the context of a signal using a lambda expression.
add:x:@.session
   .
      .
         role:system
         content:x:@signal/*/context
